["<div dir=\"rtl\" align=\"right\">\n\n\n <table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; margin-left: -52.65pt\" dir=\"rtl\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\">\n  <tr style=\"height: 22.7pt\">\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   خبت نار جسمي باشتعال منارتي</td>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">\n   <font face=\"Arial\"><b>\n   <span style=\"font-family: Al-Sadiq Bold\" lang=\"AR-SA\">&nbsp;</span></b></font></td>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">\n   فأظلم عيشي إذ أضاء شهابها</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">\n   أيا بومة قد عششت فوق هامتي</td>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">\n   <font face=\"Arial\"><b>\n   <span style=\"font-family: Al-Sadiq Bold\" lang=\"AR-SA\">&nbsp;</span></b></font></td>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">\n   على الرغم مني حين طار غرابها</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">\n   رأيت خراب العمر مني فزرتني</td>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">\n   <font face=\"Arial\"><b>\n   <span style=\"font-family: Al-Sadiq Bold\" lang=\"AR-SA\">&nbsp;</span></b></font></td>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;و \n   مأواك من كل الديار خرابها</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;أ \n   أنعم عيشا بعد ما حل عارضي\n   </td>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">\n   <font face=\"Arial\"><b>\n   <span style=\"font-family: Al-Sadiq Bold\" lang=\"AR-SA\">&nbsp;</span></b></font></td>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">\n   طلائع شيب ليس يغني خضابها</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\" height=\"25\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">\n   و غرة عمر المرء قبل مشيبه</td>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\" height=\"25\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">\n   <font face=\"Arial\"><b>\n   <span style=\"font-family: Al-Sadiq Bold\" lang=\"AR-SA\">&nbsp;</span></b></font></td>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\" height=\"25\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">\n   و قد فنيت نفس تولى شبابها</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;إذا \n   اصفر وجه المرء و ابيض رأسه</td>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">\n   <font face=\"Arial\"><b>\n   <span style=\"font-family: Al-Sadiq Bold\" lang=\"AR-SA\">&nbsp;</span></b></font></td>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">\n   تنغص من أيامه مستطابها</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;و \n   أد زكاة الجاه و اعلم بأنها\n   </td>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">\n   <font face=\"Arial\"><b>\n   <span style=\"font-family: Al-Sadiq Bold\" lang=\"AR-SA\">&nbsp;</span></b></font></td>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">\n   كمثل زكاة المال تم نصابها</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr style=\"height: 22.7pt\">\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;و \n   أحسن إلى الأحرار تملك رقابهم</td>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">\n   <font face=\"Arial\"><b>\n   <span style=\"font-family: Al-Sadiq Bold\" lang=\"AR-SA\">&nbsp;</span></b></font></td>\n   <td style=\" padding-left: 5.4pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; padding-top: 0cm; padding-bottom: 0cm\" align=\"center\">\n   <p style=\"text-kashida: 0%\" dir=\"RTL\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\">\n   فخير تجارات الكريم اكتسابها</td>\n  </tr>\n    </table>\n  \n</div>\n","ديوان الإمام علي(ع)"]